==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Thenar
<hw>The"nar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>The palm of the hand.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>The
prominence of the palm above the base of the thumb; the thenar eminence;
the ball of the thumb. Sometimes applied to the corresponding part of
the foot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thenardite</ent>⟦br⟧
